---
// Final CTA — start a build
---

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta">
      <div class="cta__inner">
        <span class="section-eyebrow" style="justify-content: center;">Start a Build</span>
        <h2>Ready to play your own?</h2>
        <p>
          Guitars take approximately 6 months to build. A 50% deposit secures
          your build slot, then photos of your guitar's progress are sent to
          you throughout the entire process.
        </p>
        <p class="cta__scarcity">
          Dean personally builds every guitar. Only a limited number of build
          slots open each year — early inquiry holds your place in the queue.
        </p>
        <a href="mailto:info@dccustomguitars.com?subject=Custom%20Build%20Inquiry" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">
          Get in Touch
        </a>
        <div>
          <a href="mailto:info@dccustomguitars.com" class="cta__email">
            info@dccustomguitars.com
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
